---
  Loops/While

  https://rosettacode.org/wiki/Loops/While

  === Task ===
  Start an integer value at 1024.
  Loop while it is greater than zero.
  Print the value (with a newline) and divide it by two each time through the loop.
---

func main() -> {
    let $n = 1024;

    while n > 0 do {
        println n;
        n = n / 2;
    };
};